articles.title: ‘Five Nights at Freddy’s’ Review: Josh Hutcherson and a Crew of Killer Puppets in a Scare-Free Bore Fest - Hollywood Reporter
articles.description: The giant animatronic animal figures at a family pizza restaurant come to murderous life in Blumhouse's horror film, whose cast also includes Mary Stuart Masterson and Matthew Lillard.
